Package: survregVB
Title: Variational Bayesian Analysis of Survival Data Using a Log-Logistic Accelerated Failure Time Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Alison", "Zhang", , "alisonxzhang@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package implements an alternative approach to MCMC methods and infers the parameters of the log-
    logistic AFT model via a mean-field variational Bayes (VB) algorithm. A piecewise approximation technique is 
    embedded in deriving the VB algorithm to achieve conjugacy. 
